{"tid":2092874,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"小熊維尼在中國安享晚年","createTime":"2020-07-03T12:52:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T13:05:09.000Z","uid":291835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"54999e880264d886f9a7c852095224b6237e9112","tid":2092874,"uid":291835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T12:52:32.000Z","msg":"「這種原始殘忍的取膽方法在中國居然是合法的，在東北、四川、廣西等地的熊廠還是大量採用。抽膽時有一種劇痛，慘叫的熊實在是不能忍受的。」......<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KDx6BiM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKDx6BiM.jpg&h=1c85c2f2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n....通常在養熊場內，膽汁是每天在黑熊進食前抽取一到兩次，因為此時的膽汁的濃稠度較高。每次平均抽取30至160毫升。有些大的養熊場稱他們一天能取四次膽汁。.....<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OCd5RSb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOCd5RSb.jpg&h=544d3693&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n唔知小熊維尼會唔會有呢一日"},{"pid":"1c553238fb580e03944106422ecdb5fd17ceb55f","tid":2092874,"uid":15636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T12:55:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b049295dfacf8f8de5df7de32f668300a4cda6","tid":2092874,"uid":83990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T12:56:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc0dff69be5831ccb8ed3fe93f665bc2b3e4f3b","tid":2092874,"uid":15605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T12:59:35.000Z","msg":"雜總個膽咁細，恰下香港就叻，何來膽汁"},{"pid":"9f78db4bedb509357c7971f113166aa97fb5ba3a","tid":2092874,"uid":37413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T12:59:56.000Z","msg":"睇過紀錄片呢啲好撚慘，好唔人道，冇人性"},{"pid":"f5e1903580a3bfdf2934f78a60af7db09e901921","tid":2092874,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T13:04:01.000Z","msg":"正仆街黎<br />\n中藥害人害物"},{"pid":"c5b370187325ce601b04797e4116a6